<plot>Spoof of 'Snow White and the Seven Dwarfs (1937)' (qv) with an all-black cartoon cast. Many WWII references, including rationing (the evil Queen is a hoarder of sugar and rubber tires) and Jeep vehicles (the Sebben Dwarfs come to the rescue in three of them). Also spoofs the extreme close-up of Kane's lips uttering "Rosebud" in 'Citizen Kane (1941)' (qv).</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?109540</url></doc>
